---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const updated = 'July 8, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How EV Auto Pro collects, uses and protects your personal information."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14 lg:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          EV Auto Pro is operated by Shandong Wencai Import &amp; Export Co., Ltd. (山东稳彩进出口有限公司),
          a vehicle export company registered in the People's Republic of China. This policy explains how we
          handle personal information collected through evautopro.com.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">When you submit an inquiry or quote request, we collect the information you provide:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Name and company name</li>
          <li>Email address and WhatsApp / phone number</li>
          <li>Country or region and target market</li>
          <li>Vehicle models, quantities and other requirements you describe</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">
          We also receive standard technical data with each form submission, such as your IP address,
          approximate country and browser type, which we use for spam prevention.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>To respond to your inquiry and prepare quotations</li>
          <li>To communicate with you about orders, shipping and documentation</li>
          <li>To maintain internal records of business inquiries</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">4. Where Your Data Is Processed</h2>
        <p>
          Inquiry data is delivered to our team through our website hosting provider and business
          communication tools, and may be processed on servers located outside your country, including
          in China. We keep inquiry records only as long as needed for business communication and
          legal record-keeping.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You may request a copy of the personal information we hold about you, ask us to correct it,
          or ask us to delete it. Contact us at
          <a href="mailto:gacaicai@gmail.com" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">gacaicai@gmail.com</a>
          and we will respond within a reasonable time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          See our <a href="/legal/cookies/" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a> for
          details on the cookies used by this site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on
          this page with the date of the last revision.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
